summary: Adds much more detail to the city of solitude
descriptionHtml:
Expands the Beauty of Skyrim Solitude with more Details. Adds new objects in almost every place in the city, and makes it dense and beautiful. More Foliage, shrubs, trees, waterfalls, pools, places to relax. 

Credits to: tx3000 for fixing a really big error inside this mod. thanks to tx3000 again!! 
Credits to: GKB Green Trees by Ga-Knomboe Boy; thank you for your amazing work. 

Please report any error, hint, idea. i will take that into account for future changes. 

Have fun!!
author: beachboy1969
